  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and in shtebl, there was a library that you wouldn't fit into this house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of it, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], if you know what it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a-- it was a lot going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] There was still the-- it was a-- it was-- it was a library.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could study there 24 hours a day and-- and never-- never get tired of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was sometimes came-- came a-- a troop to Chrzanów.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a child, not-- not-- not in a theater.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was--I was in a group-- we didn't go to theaters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we went-- sometimes there was a Purim thing, or Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- it was-- a group came to-- just to make-- make a party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was customary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, customary-- we did [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did all the things, which was-- we did even annoy people in [INAUDIBLE] to throw them those things which annoys them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I feel sorry for them, but that-- this was the custom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, this-- this-- those little [INAUDIBLE] in the beards?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this-- this-- this was a part of-- of-- of the-- of the fun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- elementary school before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was-- it was 13. 11, 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I studied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The most thing, I studied a few years in-- in the shtebl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I belonged there.",
