      "text": "I belonged there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- I learned [NON-ENGLISH] for a few years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I went to Sosnowice and [NON-ENGLISH], which I studied there for a year and a half.",
